pageProduct.name: Nutra-Life Bilberry 10000 Plus 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

This high-strength eye health support formula combines the herbs Bilberry and Grape seed with Lutein and Betacarotene. Lutein supports macula and retina health and Vitamin C maintains capillary health.

Suitable For: Eye health, vision, macular support

Size: 60 tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Eye Health Support
• Contains Lutein to aid healthy eye function

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Each tablet provides: Herbal extracts equiv.:
Vaccinium myrtillus (Bilberry) fruit fresh 10g, Stand. equiv.
Anthocyanosides 36mg, Vitis vinifera (Grape) seed dry 3g.
Lutein 6mg, Betacarotene 3mg, Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 263mg,
Riboflavin (Vitamin B2) 25mg, Nicotinamide (B3) 10mg,
d-alpha-Tocopheryl acid succinate (Vitamin E 75 IU) 62.6mg, Taurine
50mg, Glutamine 25mg, Citrus bioflavonoids extract 50mg, Rutoside
50mg, Chromium (as chromic chloride hexahydrate) 50µg, Zinc
(as amino acid chelate) 15mg, Tabletting aids, Colour.

Contains: Contains: Animal product, benzoates, soya bean products.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Wheat

Directions

RECOMMENDED ADULT DOSAGE: Take 1 tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare
professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place below 30°C.
